==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: Hand over the money with one hand, get the goods with the other hand.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: yī shǒu jiāo qián, yī shǒu jiāo huò

===Idiom===
'''[[一]][[手]][[交]][[錢]]，[[一]][[手]][[交]][[貨]]'''

# Do things in a simple and direct manner.

===Alternate forms===
[[一手交钱，一手交货]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

